{"tid":2411747,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"數學是種族主義  正確的答案為白人至上文化","createTime":"2021-02-17T14:22:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T15:04:59.000Z","uid":225931,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bba3cf6579e21c760d9a3138252dbb3e68849c47","tid":2411747,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:22:36.000Z","msg":"俄勒岡州教育局（ODE）2月13日推出一個給教師使用的&ldquo;工具包&rdquo;，在網上引起熱議。 起因是ODE的這個培訓計劃，教導老師如何&ldquo;減少數學中的種族主義&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n這個名為&ldquo;公平數學&rdquo;的教學指導有82頁，該計劃認為&ldquo;準確的數學是白人至上文化的種族主義內容&rdquo;，白人至高無上體現在尋找正確答案上。 &ldquo;集中精力獲得正確的答案&rdquo;以及&ldquo;要求學生展示工作&rdquo;被視為白人至上文化&ldquo;滲透數學課堂&rdquo;的方式。<br />\n<br />\n該工具包還鼓勵教師採用&ldquo;中心民族數學&rdquo;，具體包括各種指南，其中之一指示教育工作者&ldquo;確定和挑戰數學用於維護資本主義、帝國主義和種族主義觀點的方式&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><a href=\"https://docdro.id/FMEYtgL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocdro.id%2FFMEYtgL&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN26y4iG8TIfC1p449sO1N5Ck%3D&h=f57bf50c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docdro.id/FMEYtgL</a></strong>"},{"pid":"5c60e9671b5c085b92570b3b9cb986b26bc23da2","tid":2411747,"uid":225931,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:23:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Zh3Yz3PiXZw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZh3Yz3PiXZw&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN26y4iG8TIfC1p449sO1N5Ck%3D&h=1bff6e2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Zh3Yz3PiXZw</a>"},{"pid":"47543dd4dcf212b718443172d34367e3f6212417","tid":2411747,"uid":225931,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:49:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iKcWu0tsiZM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiKcWu0tsiZM&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN26y4iG8TIfC1p449sO1N5Ck%3D&h=a4fcd212\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iKcWu0tsiZM</a>"},{"pid":"ea3624ef9b4